               <title>PRODUCT WARNINGS AND PRECAUTIONS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>DO NOT SMOKE NEAR THIS UNIT.  KEEP AWAY FROM HEAT, FLAME OR SPARKS.  KEEP UNIT WELL VENTILATED AT ALL TIMES.  DO NOT TOUCH FROSTED PARTS.  KEEP UNIT IN UPRIGHT POSITION.  READ PATIENT OPERATING INSTRUCTIONS.<br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
